title: Morning Joe 1/22/21
description: Dr. Anthony Fauci, one of the government’s top public health experts, signaled that he feels free to speak honestly about Covid-19 now that former President Donald Trump is out of office. The Morning Joe panel discusses his appearance at Thursday's press briefing.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
